Audience Analytics 
Mobile Solutions



































Mobile first. Second nature.


Mobile has changed how we connect. It’s the first device you turn to for nearly every need. It’s instinctively part of us. At comScore, we’ve been measuring audiences across devices from the start. It’s our second nature. 











Mobile is our primary tool.


Mobile devices account for more than 60% of digital time in the majority of global markets, but to what degree are handheld devices altering human behaviour?Mobile's Hierarchy of Needs – a data-packed comScore global report – explores how mobile has become a primary platform, not simply replacing desktop activity, but creating new patterns of digital interaction and new considerations for advertisers, agencies and publishers.Download Report



 





We can help you in a mobile-first world.




Understand your audience consumption across devices.Get a complete, unduplicated view of how audiences consume content across smartphones, tablets and desktops. With Media Metrix® Multi-Platform and Mobile Metrix®, gain insight into key metrics such as unique visitors, time spent and demographics.Request a demo 






Improve the performance of your mobile ad campaigns.Validate the delivery of your advertising campaigns for display and video to ensure your ads are viewable, brand safe and free from invalid traffic with validated Campaign Essentials™.Request a demo

 








Better know your mobile audiences' behaviours and attitudes.Gain a deeper view of your mobile audiences' behaviours, purchase intent and interests with MobiLens® or get tailored mobile insights to address your unique business needs with our custom solutions. Learn more about available solutions in your market.Contact us 






Gain insight into how your audiences watch video differently across devices.Better understand how, when and where digital video content is consumed across smartphones, tablets and desktops with Video Metrix® Multi-Platform.Request a demo

 






Why comScore




Massive ScaleGlobal coverage through the comScore census network, mobile and desktop panels.

Multi-Platform AudiencesFirst to measure unduplicated audiences across desktop, smartphone and tablets.

Trusted ExperienceOver 17 years measuring audiences around the world.We have your needs covered across the world.Audience and campaign measurement across multiple markets.

Market coverageArgentina, Australia, Austria, Belgium, Brazil, Canada, Chile, China, Colombia, Denmark, Finland, France, Germany, Hong Kong, India, Indonesia, Ireland, Israrel, Italy, Japan, Malaysia, Mexico, Netherlands, New Zealand, Norway, Peru, Philippines, Poland, Portugal, Puerto Rico, Russia, Singapore, South Africa, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, Taiwan, Thailand, Turkey, United Kingdom, United States, Uruguay, Venezuela, Vietnam. 






Ready to learn more?
Contact us today to learn how comScore can help you.
