The Search Monitor Vs. Ad Monitoring Providers
See why our SEM, SEO & PLA monitoring tools are the most precise in the industry 


Looking at competitive ad monitoring providers such as SEMrush, SpyFu, and comScore? Ask yourself:
1)  Do I get daily monitoring of SEM, SEO & PLAs?
 2)  Can I control geo-targets to identify hard-to-find violations?
 3)  Can I target locally at the zip code or city / DMA level?
 4)  Can I customize the data to meet specific report requests?
 5)  Can I get unlimited keywords or access to the Lighthouse keyword library?
The Search Monitor provides all of the above. Check out our features below:


THE SEARCH MONITOROTHER PROVIDERS
 DAILY AD CRAWLINGYES
We crawl ads and listings daily (even hourly, if needed!)NOCONFIGURABLE GEO-TARGETS WITH LOCAL TARGETINGYES
Coverage by city, DMA, state & countryNO REPORT CUSTOMIZATIONYES
Custom reports & charts using your own metrics, competitors, and partnersNOUNLIMITED KEYWORD PACKAGESYES
No limits to the size of your keyword listNO LIGHTHOUSEYES
Access to 1,200 keyword groups from our Lighthouse library
NO

 
Put us to the test! Tell us the providers you’re considering (examples: SEMrush, SpyFu & comScore) and we’ll show you a detailed comparison using data on your keywords or product category.
Request a Demo     Contact Us For A Comparison






